OL,4,CFrench drone tourist in Iran Benjamin
OL,5,CBriere 'facing spy charges'
OL,6, A French tourist detained in Iran ten
OL,7, months ago is facing two charges of
OL,8, "spying and propaganda against the
OL,9, system", according to his lawyer.
OL,11,FBenjamin Briere, 35, was arrested after
OL,12,Fflying a drone near the
OL,13,FIran-Turkmenistan border.
OL,15,FHis lawyer Saeid Dehghan said Mr Briere
OL,16,Fcould face a long prison sentence if
OL,17,Ffound guilty.
OL,19,FIt comes at a time of rising tensions
OL,20,Fbetween Iran and European countries and
OL,21,Fthe US over Iran's nuclear capacity.
